            "\n\nO Allah, suffice me with what is lawful against what is unlawful, and enrich me by Your bounty from needing anyone besides You.\n",
            "\n\nAnd the Prophet ﷺ said:\nO Allah, make the most abundant provision You grant me at the end of my life and when my age is greatest.\n",
